  Head to Felwithe inside the zone there are  10 guards that spawn/roam throughout the bottom of zone.  Those guards are EXTREMELY easy to down with epic(no effort involved at all really) and they drop those nifty 2hand plain jane swords right.  Well just find your most favorable vendor and cash those babies in for a whopping 21pp a piece.  That's what i get at the Bazaar vendors with a CHA of 130 . Summon a slew of 100% WR bags and go to town for a few<br>
